{
  "DARV.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "这里像撤景后的仓库。道具堆得到处都是……我认得几套，是我穿过的。",
  "DARV.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "哈哈！剧组散场了，东西归我！挑一件顺手的——反正下一幕也不知道要演谁！",
  "DARV.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你又来翻箱倒柜？放心，盔甲和笏板都还在。今天演文戏还是武戏？",
  "DARV.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "我翻遍了仓库，也没找到写着“真实身份”的道具……",
  "DARV.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "DARV.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……若真有那样东西，大概也不会放在显眼处。龙套演员的东西，通常都在角落。",
  "DARV.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "说得对。拿这个吧——至少下一幕换场时，你还能记得自己曾拿过什么。",

  "NEOW.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "没有布景，没有镜头……《新・三国演义》的最终场，却还要我向上走。",
  "NEOW.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "[sine]...导演... ..进去了..... \n...编剧... ..也进去了..... \n...现在... ..轮到... ..你.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "[sine]...你又... ..开机了..... \n...这一遍... ..和上一遍... ..不一样.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "[sine]...还缺... ..什么...？[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "祈求",
  "NEOW.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "若你一定要把东西写进剧本……请让我分得清，哪些记忆属于演员，哪些属于角色。",
  "NEOW.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "[sine]...去吧... \n..塔顶... ..有写剧本的..... \n..东西.....[/sine]",

  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你这里……假发、妆镜、满墙的脸谱。我演过的脸，好像都挂在这里。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "哎呀，龙套也要上镜呀。来，让我把你打扮成今天最像主角的样子。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "将军的眉、哨兵的眼、说客的笑……你今天打算让哪一张脸上场？",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "若我把你妆成「真实的自己」，你猜天意会不会满意？",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "婉拒",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……我没有自己的脸可以给你化。有的只是一堆借来的五官。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "那就带着这些脸走吧。反正下一幕，它们还会抢着替你说话。",

  "OROBAS.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你跳来跳去……是在改分镜，还是在改我的台词？",
  "OROBAS.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "都在改！！都在改！！剧本、走位、人格——全乱成一锅粥了！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "别急！！上一秒你是大将军，下一秒你是小公公——这才叫天意！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "给你个东西！！想要“下一页剧本还没翻”的那一秒吗？！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "OROBAS.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……我只想要一页不再自行修改的剧本。",
  "OROBAS.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "没有那种东西！！但乱一点也好——乱到连天意都来不及做出修正！！",

  "PAEL.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "我演过很多尸体……躺下的时候，反而最安静。",
  "PAEL.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "[thinky_dots]那就再躺一会儿……在还没轮到你说话之前……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "[thinky_dots]醒着的人要记台词……睡着的人只要等场记来喊……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]所以你「能不能不逃了」……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回答",
  "PAEL.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……我不能躺太久。剧组里，龙套一躺下，就容易被当成真的死了。",
  "PAEL.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "[thinky_dots]那就带着这个走……至少下一幕开始前……你还能假装还没被叫到.....[/thinky_dots]",

  "TANX.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "武行替身……临时顶上。这一场，我先死，还是你先上？",
  "TANX.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "[b]别废话！！拿着武器！！没有排练就照打！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "[b]那个演将军的还来吗？！让他出来打！！别总让龙套扛武戏！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "[b]天意要咆哮、要自刎、要酒！！它不要演员！！那就演给它看！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "退让",
  "TANX.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……我知道这一切是戏。可我的肌肉记得怎么挥刀，那是借来的记忆。",
  "TANX.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "[b]好！！那就用借来的手去打！！打到塔顶！！看天意还怎么改你的剧本！！[/b]",

  "TEZCATARA.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "火堆……像剧组收工后的取暖。可这里连盒饭都没有。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "没有盒饭也没关系呀。来，让[jitter][b]热酒[/b][/jitter]为你暖暖身子。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你背着的不是行李，是还没卸下的[jitter][b]角色[/b][/jitter]吧？要不要在这里先放下一张脸？",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "尝尝这个吧。凉掉之前，还像一顿像样的收工饭。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "推辞",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……我不饿。空着肚子，反而比较像龙套——没人记得有没有喂过你。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "那就只坐一会儿。等火灭了，再继续向上——通告单上可没写休息多久。",

  "VAKUU.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你也做交易？那你要我的什么……姓名，记忆，还是「龙套演员」这四个字？",
  "VAKUU.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "最便宜的，是你以为还属于自己的那一点[sine]自我[/sine]……",
  "VAKUU.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "我见过很多卖灵魂的人。你比较特别——你连灵魂有几份都数不清。",
  "VAKUU.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "如果在合同末尾写一行小字：允许你永远扮演别人——你签吗？",
  "VAKUU.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "VAKUU.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……我签不起。我要找的是天意——然后拒绝被安排好的角色。",
  "VAKUU.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "有志气。拿去吧——但愿你分得清，哪一份代价是哪一个「你」付的。",

  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0r.ancient": "尖塔里没有场记，没有摄影师。只有你，和一张写着你名字的通告单。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-0r.next": "回答",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1r.char": "龙套演员，饰……龙套演员。通告单上只写了“向上”——没给台词，也没给分镜。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-2r.ancient": "台词会自己找来。天意从不关注演员和剧本——它只关注世界线的修正。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.0-attack": "Both",

  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你又站在这里。是补拍，还是天意对上一版结局不满意？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-1r.char": "同一场戏，第二次拍。我内心的死刑犯还在和刽子手抢位置——场记却还没来。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-2r.ancient": "那就继续演。只要塔还在，就没有真正杀青这回事。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.1-attack": "Both",

  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0r.ancient": "快到最后一场了。导演、编剧、天意……总该有一个在塔顶。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1r.char": "他们都有姓名、经历和结局。只有我负责扮演他们。\n[i][font_size=22]把所有角色都演完以后，剩下的……会是我吗？[/font_size][/i]",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_UNIVERSE_CHARACTER_SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-2r.ancient": "上去问天意。若它还需要玉玺、尸体和替身，它就不需要演员真正离开角色——你要做的，是拒绝只做被安排好的那一个。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.SUNQIAN_CHARACTER.2-attack": "Both"
}
